description:
In this mini-episode, Kate and Doree share listener stories about acts of kindness, hear from a caller who is struggling to ask for help, discuss friend-making as adults, and receive the perfect suggestion for an episode sign-off.  


To leave a voicemail for a future episode, call 781-591-0390. You can also email the podcast at forever35podcast@gmail.com.
